<doc id="619970" wikidata="Q5149571" url="?curid=619970" title="Columbia, Iowa">
<text>Columbia is an unincorporated community in Marion County, Iowa, United States.

==History==
The population of Columbia was 160 in 1940.

==References==</text><links>
