<doc id="619986" wikidata="Q3254762" url="?curid=619986" title="List of Rotterdam Metro stations">
<text>The following is the list of the 70 stations on the Rotterdam Metro system in Rotterdam, Netherlands. The Rotterdam Metro has five metro lines, lines A through E. Line E is also referred to by the brand name RandstadRail, although it is operated by the same company as lines A through D. At Beurs station, one can transfer among all five lines.

